{"tid":656071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15前管理層交書面意見 批九巴營運混亂","createTime":"2018-05-07T02:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T11:03:58.000Z","uid":72280,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd499a3982027a42c9ea80cc14b6e35dd52b785","tid":656071,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:14:14.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】一群來自九巴不同部門的前管理層，向香港專營巴士服務獨立檢討委員會呈交書面意見，矛頭指向現任九巴董事總經理李澤昌（圖）自2015年1月上任後，大批有經驗員工相繼被辭退或離職，公司架構不斷重整，當中「安全及服務質量部」更被拆解不再存在。在商務及資產管理部任職的朱姓前管理人員稱，他於去年底辭職，是「不欲再在精神病院工作」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/101127_570d7fe2887fb6b0bba26bdc5b378592.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F101127_570d7fe2887fb6b0bba26bdc5b378592.png&h=2a0c2f3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年辭職者﹕不欲再在精神病院工作<br />\n<br />\n呈交書面意見的15名前九巴管理層來自不同部門，包括副車務總監程艾樂（Alok Jain），其他部門有安全及服務質量部、工程部、稽核部、商務及資產管理部、採購部、資訊科技部及企業傳訊部等，部分人匿名，有些人在九巴任職年資達25年。這些前管理層指出，決定發聲是要揭露導致九巴服務質素惡化的原因，為車禍死傷者帶來公義。<br />\n<br />\n指用人唯親 大批老臣子離職<br />\n<br />\n綜合書面意見內容，各人直指自董事總經理李澤昌2015年1月上任後，公司出現朝令夕改、用人唯親及管理混亂等情况，大批忠心及具經驗的中級和高級管理層人員相繼被辭退及自願離職，改由缺乏營運巴士經驗的人擔任，結果導致公司營運混亂，經驗及技術出現斷層，員工士氣低落。<br />\n<br />\n「安全及服務質量部」被撤<br />\n<br />\n書面意見亦指，九巴原有安全及服務質量部，負責巴士日常運作安全事宜，惟李澤昌上任後該部門高層被解僱，部門被拆解不再存在。該批前管理層指現有管理層短視，只顧賺取利潤，向股東顯示表現較前管理層好。一名沒公開姓名的現職員工以一輛巴士形容公司，稱「九巴原本就像一架穩妥而設備優良的巴士，現在一天一天被拆去螺絲和零件，終有一天拋錨在街上或車毁人亡」。<br />\n<br />\n2014年主要行政人員<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/101346_36f21dd97d431facfa92be55cde4a693.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F101346_36f21dd97d431facfa92be55cde4a693.png&h=f8bb4a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017 ：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/101246_f0dd881a6931a74a25c253a65cc4de39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F101246_f0dd881a6931a74a25c253a65cc4de39.png&h=e43d676b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a5ad1e25e0be0b6e9976317de7142b303eecdfb","tid":656071,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e550e8d7a5a201c205831ca5b9fbd26c53e002ac","tid":656071,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25ef2033bc5d25e317774193a3d923894b8a82b","tid":656071,"uid":72280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"原文<br />\nSource: 巴士服務獨立檢討委員會意見書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/115022_2e4f0743d182b178c83f45f55787dfdc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F115022_2e4f0743d182b178c83f45f55787dfdc.png&h=0d2ec116&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/115023_eae131cf2ab0713a648fcd1041f3af75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F115023_eae131cf2ab0713a648fcd1041f3af75.png&h=0b268e34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/115024_304fb96a0463f28c2906cb644860083e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F115024_304fb96a0463f28c2906cb644860083e.png&h=860e2db0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/07/115025_1bf53cf026ebe3fd43c2b899fba9607a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2F115025_1bf53cf026ebe3fd43c2b899fba9607a.png&h=60744abe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.es